results.deck: DreamCatcher is a Toronto based game publisher.
results.description:
DreamCatcher Interactive Inc. is a Ontario, Canada based video game publisher. The company was acquired by Austrian JoWood Productions, in 2006.

Labels

DreamCatcher publishes its games under several labels:

  • The DreamCatcher name is used for Action, FPS, Strategy and Role Playing games.
  • The Adventure Company label is used for publishing the company's adventure games.
  • Some of DreamCatcher's action games are published under the DCi Games label.
